31:22.400 --> 31:24.000
Of course you'll see nothing.

31:24.080 --> 31:27.880
"Convenience store
around the corner"? Really?

31:27.960 --> 31:30.560
"People don't change,
they reveal themselves."

31:31.200 --> 31:33.200
"It won't be the first time
I've seen you naked."

31:35.360 --> 31:38.040
