of being naked in front of him?

33:03.520 --> 33:05.640
Look, Vanessa.

33:06.200 --> 33:11.320
Stare like someone who wants to see,
like someone who really wants to.

33:12.760 --> 33:16.120
He could be one of those guys
who would take you

33:16.200 --> 33:18.800
to a motel afterwards with round beds,

33:18.880 --> 33:24.440
and then you'd go to eat greasy toast
at 5:00 a.m. in some trailer.

33:25.440 --> 33:27.800
But wanting it, you know?

33:28.800 --> 33:30.240
Come on, Vanessa.

33:30.320 --> 33:32.520
I know it's been many years,

33:33.480 --> 33:37.120
but your last name
doesn't mean "passion" for nothing.

33:38.240 --> 33:40.440
