watching that wedding show.

35:18.560 --> 35:19.440
<i>Love Your Neighbor.</i>

35:19.520 --> 35:20.400
That's the one.

35:20.880 --> 35:23.000
I was watching that, and I thought,

35:23.920 --> 35:26.520
"Good thing I have my SatysFire."

35:27.080 --> 35:28.960
-Satis-what?
-And then I thought,

35:29.040 --> 35:33.000
"What Vanessa needs at this stage
is not a man,

35:33.080 --> 35:35.360
it's a SatysFire."

35:36.760 --> 35:39.400
German technology. Never failed me.

35:39.480 --> 35:44.160
But just in case, I had another
brand new one at home. It's yours.

35:45.520 --> 35:49.040
SatysFire Pro 2 Next Generation.

35:49.120 --> 35:52.000
The review
in the British <i>Cosmopolitan</i> said,

35:52.080 --> 35:55.080
"Jesus Christ! I'll never go out again."

35:57.560 --> 36:01.400
Imagine that your clitoris is music.

36:02.320 --> 36:04.240
All the music ever made.

36:05.080 --> 36:06.560
When it comes to music,

36:06.640 --> 36:10.640
