the triangle on a folklore dance group,

36:10.720 --> 36:14.640
or, at best,
they'll do a solo on the harmonica.

36:16.120 --> 36:21.040
But SatysFire is the Vienna Orchestra

36:21.120 --> 36:23.520
playing "Ride of the Valkyries."

36:24.360 --> 36:29.920
It's percussion. It's wind instruments.
