37:27.440 --> 37:29.480
-I declare you--
-You can kiss each other!

37:44.320 --> 37:45.240
Thank you.

38:11.960 --> 38:13.720
Capristano.

38:13.800 --> 38:16.040
Montevelho.

38:48.000 --> 38:49.720
May your love

38:50.640 --> 38:55.520
never be sabotaged by tiny people.

38:57.160 --> 38:59.960
Only people of low moral stature

39:01.920 --> 39:05.040
won't recognize their smallness.

39:07.160 --> 39:13.880
Dwarfism can also be a heart disease.

39:14.440 --> 39:16.200
As the poet said,

39:16.280 --> 39:22.080
"To be great, be whole."

39:22.160 --> 39:25.280
The poet didn't say,
"To be tiny, be whole."

39:25.360 --> 39:26.360
No, no, no.

39:26.440 --> 39:29.920
The poet didn't say,
"To be small, be whole."

39:30.720 --> 39:32.840
He didn't say, "To be minimal, be whole."

39:32.920 --> 39:36.000
No, the poet said,
"To be great, be whole."

39:36.640 --> 39:39.920
He didn't say,
"To be tiny, be a quarter, be half."

39:40.000 --> 39:41.440
No! "To be great…

39:42.920 --> 39:43.920
Great."

39:50.760 --> 39:51.720
Thank you.

